docs.abstract: The software giant faces mounting pressure from activist investors and pushback from employees unhappy about a wave of firings and the scaling back of office perks.
docs.snippet: The software giant faces mounting pressure from activist investors and pushback from employees unhappy about a wave of firings and the scaling back of office perks.
docs.lead_paragraph: Wednesday’s earnings report by Salesforce may be the most closely watched in the software giant’s 24-year history. Investors — especially the now half-dozen activist shareholders who are clamoring for change at the company, and possibly board seats — will be eager to hear how its chief, Marc Benioff, plans to turn around its fortunes.

headline.main: The Heat on Salesforce Grows Ahead of a Big Earnings Call

docs.abstract: President Biden is expected to use his first veto to protect environmental, social and corporate governance investment considerations in retirement plans.
docs.snippet: President Biden is expected to use his first veto to protect environmental, social and corporate governance investment considerations in retirement plans.
docs.lead_paragraph: Senate Republicans, helped by two Democratic defectors, voted on Wednesday to block a Labor Department rule allowing retirement plan managers to include environmental, social and corporate governance considerations (E.S.G., for short) in their investment plans.

headline.main: The Battle Over E.S.G. Heads to the White House

docs.abstract: First Citizens agreed on Sunday to acquire the failed lender’s retail operations. Will the move convince investors that recent turmoil in the sector is over?
docs.snippet: First Citizens agreed on Sunday to acquire the failed lender’s retail operations. Will the move convince investors that recent turmoil in the sector is over?
docs.lead_paragraph: First Citizens agreed on Sunday night to buy most of Silicon Valley Bank at a discount, clearing the way for the U.S. banking industry to potentially move on from the turmoil set off by the collapse of the tech-focused lender.

headline.main: Markets Climb as Silicon Valley Bank Finally Finds a Buyer
